name: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Superior Court of Pennsylvania, Common Pleas Court of Philadelphia, Denis P. Cohen, Respondents v. Donald BETHEA, Petitioner

parties: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Superior Court of Pennsylvania, Common Pleas Court of Philadelphia, Denis P. Cohen, Respondents v. Donald BETHEA, Petitioner.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 23rd day of March, 2016, the Application for Extraordinary Jurisdiction, the “Motion Objection to Superior Court Order[s],” and the “Motion to Adjudicate Criminal Contempt” are DENIED, and the Prothonotary is DIRECTED to strike the name of the jurist from the caption.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
